704849f-a.title: Brooklyn: Henry Street - Degraw Street
704849f-a.text:
480-492 Henry Street at the S.W. corner of Degraw Street. TThe view
shows a garage which in 1908 was known as the Pilgrims Chapel (no
denomination) and in 1916 as the Oriole Theatre.
February 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
